name: Metaverse
description: Created in 2002 for Entertainment Weekly magazine for an article on #nealstephenson ’s seminal novel, #snowcrash; wherein the phrase “metaverse” was coined.   And here we are, today, really on our way there. It’s quite possible this very illustration will find itself “hanging” in the #metaverse any day now.
